
## docker installation
   yum install docker -y
   systemctl start docker
   systemctl status docker

## docker-compose install :- Docker-compose is an tool of docker docker-compose require saperate installation.

   sudo curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.22.0/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m) -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

##  NOTE: to get the latest version
    sudo curl -L https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/latest/download/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m) -o /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

##  Fix permissions after download:
sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/docker-compose

## Docker Compose is installed in a different location: The error message specifies the path
  /usr/local/bin/docker-compose up

  
  
